2.00	Abigail,_Har_Hebron	Avigayil	Abigail (Hebrew: ‎‎) is an Israeli settlement located adjacent to Ma'on in the Judean Hills of the West Bank. The village receives its municipal services from the Har Hebron Regional Council. Abigail is named after the Biblical Abigail, the wife of Nabal, who lived in the original Ma'on.	
